{
  "page": "Nute the Barber",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Nute the Barber</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Nute the Barber by cloudninja9.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ac/Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg/350px-Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ac/Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg/525px-Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ac/Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg/700px-Nute_the_Barber_by_cloudninja9.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Nute the Barber by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cloudninja9.deviantart.com/\">cloudninja9</a>©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nNute the Barber</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oakenshield\" title=\"Lord of Oakenshield\">Lord of Oakenshield</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafnute.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafnute.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Nute the Barber</b> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> raider and the best man of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a>'s crew aboard the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Victory\" title=\"Iron Victory\">Iron Victory</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Nute\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Nute</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Nute\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Nute</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Nute\" title=\"Category:Images of Nute\">Images of Nute</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Nute the Barber is a thickset man with bandy legs and long arms. His eyes are growing weak.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Nute is a noted warrior<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> who wields throwing axes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Nute earned his nickname of \"the Barber\" due to his ability in his youth to throw an axe so well that it was said he could shave you with it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Nute the Barber accompanies <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Nagga%27s_Cradle\" title=\"Nagga&#39;s Cradle\">Nagga's Cradle</a>, and he squints to identify the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> ships already in the bay. When the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Captain_of_the_Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Lord Captain of the Iron Fleet\">Lord Captain of the Iron Fleet</a> departs <i><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Victory\" title=\"Iron Victory\">Iron Victory</a></i> for the shore, he charges Nute with guarding their chests of treasure.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> During the feast that night, <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a> drinks Nute's wine after he passes out drunk.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Nute is one of Victarion's champions during the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a>, and he displays the Lord Captain's steel axe to the ironborn. Nute tries to stop Asha from climbing up the steps to present her own candidacy, but she wrenches free.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>, Victarion's older brother, is eventually chosen as the new <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_North\" title=\"King of the Isles and the North\">King of the Isles and the North</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Nute is among Victarion's crew that boards the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Serry\" title=\"House Serry\">Serry</a> ship during the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">taking of the Shields</a>, and he kills a man with a throwing axe. Victarion then gives the deck of <i>Iron Victory</i> to Nute before going to his cabin to sleep with the <a href=\"/index.php/Dusky_woman\" title=\"Dusky woman\">dusky woman</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Victarion disapproves when he learns that Euron intends for widows and orphans from <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Hewett%27s_Town\" title=\"Lord Hewett&#39;s Town\">Lord Hewett's Town</a> to be sold as <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a> instead of taken back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Thrall\" title=\"Thrall\">thralls</a>, but Nute is more accepting of the decision.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Harlaw\" title=\"Rodrik Harlaw\">Rodrik Harlaw</a> worries about the vengeance of <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a>, but Nute mocks him for being a coward.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>During the feast in <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Hewett%27s_castle\" title=\"Lord Hewett&#39;s castle\">Lord Hewett's castle</a>, Nute is named <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oakenshield\" title=\"Lord of Oakenshield\">Lord of Oakenshield</a> by King Euron. Victarion suspects this was done to \"steal\" Nute from him. He tells Nute to refuse, but Nute, pointing out that Victarion cannot offer him the same, accepts the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lordship</a> from Euron.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Sailing toward <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, Victarion misses Nute on <i>Iron Victory</i>, as <a href=\"/index.php/Wulfe_One-Ear\" title=\"Wulfe One-Ear\">Wulfe One-Ear</a> is not as competent a sailor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Nute\">Quotes by Nute</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Nute\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The strong have always taken from the weak. <a href=\"/index.php/Thrall\" title=\"Thrall\">Thralls</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slaves</a>, it makes no matter. Their men could not defend them, so now they are ours, to do with as we will.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Nute to <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Nute</b>: The <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Crow's Eye</a> sends us forth to face the longships, whilst his own men <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_the_Shields\" title=\"Taking of the Shields\">take the castles and the villages</a> and grab all the loot and women. What has he left for us?<br />\n</p><p><b>Victarion</b>: We have the glory.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Nute</b>: Glory is good, but gold is better.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Nute and <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Euron</b>: And rise, Nute the Barber, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oakenshield\" title=\"Lord of Oakenshield\">Lord of Oakenshield</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Nute</b>: A <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>?<br />\n<b>Victarion</b>: Refuse him!<br />\n</p>\n<b>Nute</b>: Refuse him? Lands and lordship? Will you make me a lord?<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a>, Nute, and <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Nute\">Quotes about Nute</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Nute\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Nute the Barber can shave a man with a thrown axe from twenty yards away.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>By raising him to <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oakenshield\" title=\"Lord of Oakenshield\">Lord of Oakenshield</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">his brother</a> made Victarion's best man his own.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nute_the_Barber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=